thread.title: Brett Ryan

author: Brett Ryan
title: Brett Ryan
text: I love going to this place. It's very convenient and 9 out of 10 times they always have the parts in stock or they'll have it ready for me in a few days. I walk up to the counter, they know me by name, and always ask me how's my project car going and things like that. its much better than going to one of those chain link parts stores where they don't really know what they're doing and the prices are much higher.
